text: "In My Head" is a 2009 song by American singer Jason Derulo and is the second single from his self-titled debut studio album. It topped the single charts in Australia, Poland and the United Kingdom. It went to the top 10 in Canada, Germany, Ireland, Israel, New Zealand, Norway and the United States.
